== E36 M3 ==
{{Infobox Automobile generation
| name           = E36
| image          = [[Image:BMW M3 E36 purple.jpg|250px|1996 BMW M3 coupe, North American version]]
| production     = 1992&ndash;1999<br/>71,242 built<ref name="Kittler 2001 130">{{cite book |title=Deutsche Autos seit 1990, vol.5 |last=Kittler |first=Eberhard |year=2001 |publisher=Motorbuch |location=Stuttgart |isbn=3-613-02128-5 |page=130}}</ref>
| body_style     = 4-door [[sedan (car)|sedan]]<br/>2-door [[coupe]]<br/>2-door [[convertible]]
| platform       = [[BMW 3 Series (E36)|BMW E36]]
|assembly        =[[Regensburg]], [[Germany]]
| related        = [[BMW 3 Series]]
| transmission   = 5-speed [[Automatic transmission|automatic]]<br/>5-speed [[Manual transmission|manual]]<br/>6-speed [[Manual transmission|manual]]
| wheelbase      = {{Auto in|106.3|0}}<br/>Convertible: {{Auto in|106.7|0}}
| length         = {{Auto in|174.5|0}}<br/>Lightweight: {{Auto in|178.0|0}}
| height         = {{Auto in|52.6|0}}<br/>Sedan: {{Auto in|53.7|0}}
| width          = {{Auto in|67.3|0}}<br/>Sedan: {{Auto in|66.9|0}}
| weight         = {{convert|1460|kg|lb|0|abbr=on}}<br/>Convertible: {{convert|1560|kg|lb|0|abbr=on}}
| engine         = 3.0 L [[Straight-6|I6]]<br/>3.2 L [[Straight-6|I6]] (1996)
